{"tid":57501,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"2016 年 TC Candler 評選「世界最帥臉孔」金城武排第93 太陽第2","createTime":"2016-12-28T05:28:30.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-29T09:38:26.000Z","uid":9573,"like":2,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0f6f9871338ee426ff080c3b2b653646dbdba2ba","tid":57501,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T05:28:30.000Z","msg":"由美國電影網站「TC Candler」評選的一年一度全球最美麗臉蛋，看完了「2016 全球百大美女臉孔，TWICE 周子瑜排名再躍升至第 8 名！」之後，當然也要關注一下最英俊臉蛋的男性排行榜，目前仍在服役中的韓國團體 Super Junior 人氣成員東海，今年獲得了 99 名，而英國偶像團體一世代（One Direction）前成員贊恩也是公認的大帥哥，今年拿下了 91 名，台灣又有哪一些帥氣男性入選這份全球榜單呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61036/58632560cc76d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61036%2F58632560cc76d.png&h=ce86d253&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼日台混血的金城武今年獲得了 93 名，這一位 43 歲的男演員永遠都是亞洲的不老男神。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61036/5863255f7e17a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61036%2F5863255f7e17a.png&h=9ec5de74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼南韓人氣嘻哈男團「Block B」成員有權（U-Kwon）獲得了 90 名。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61036/586325627a002.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61036%2F586325627a002.png&h=cb442718&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼2015年出道的韓國男子團體「SEVENTEEN」中的中國籍成員 JUN 文俊輝獲得了 81 名。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61036/58632563960a2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61036%2F58632563960a2.png&h=cb4fb011&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼「金鋼狼」休傑克曼則獲得了 77 名。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61036/58632564d83fa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61036%2F58632564d83fa.png&h=1261e442&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼南韓團體東方神起的前成員、JYJ 的現任成員金在中一向就以俊美外型聞名，30 歲的他今年拿下了世界第 73 帥。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61036/586325668331a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61036%2F586325668331a.png&h=7e5eed7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼韓國男子組合 EXO 的前中國籍成員鹿晗，2015 年參加了中國版《Running Man》知名度再度暴增，帶有陰柔氣質的他被公認為是花美男。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61036/586325680dad7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61036%2F586325680dad7.png&h=c55cf79b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼紅遍亞洲、甚至在歐美也頗具知名度的韓國演員李敏鎬獲得了 65 名。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61036/58632569c8067.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61036%2F58632569c8067.png&h=2bf96d87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼韓國男子偶像組合 2PM 成員之一玉澤演果然是公認的大帥哥，這位 28 歲的「野獸偶像」拿下了 52 名。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61036/5863256ed56de.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61036%2F5863256ed56de.png&h=417caa89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼台灣男藝人再度入選至 48 名！你無法相信王力宏居然已經 40 歲了，歲月根本沒有在他的臉上留下任何明顯的痕跡。<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61036/586325700ee3f.png[/img\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61036%2F586325700ee3f.png%5B%2Fimg&d=wzNEviSXu2%2Bb%2FbVpVe2lf5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=4697f24b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61036/586325700ee3f.png[/img</a>"},{"pid":"b1a7c99b1670ab9eb6c814b1b53a238e727f8e06","tid":57501,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T05:29:29.000Z","msg":"▼台灣男藝人再度入選至 48 名！你無法相信王力宏居然已經 40 歲了，歲月根本沒有在他的臉上留下任何明顯的痕跡。<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61036/586325700ee3f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61036%2F586325700ee3f.png&h=458a65dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼這一次與艾瑪華森合作迪士尼真人版電影《美女與野獸》（Beauty and the Beast）的路克伊凡斯，飾演反派「獵人加斯頓」的他在戲外一直以剛硬的帥哥形象聞名，今年他也獲選了世界第 45 帥。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61036/586325713bed8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61036%2F586325713bed8.png&h=9026b660&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼南韓男子團體 EXO 的 22 歲成員 Kai 金鐘仁獲得了 44 名，今年他與知名女團 f(x) 成員 Krystal 宣告成為 2016 演藝圈新情侶檔，簡直是俊男美女的超養眼配對。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61036/58632572ae06c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61036%2F58632572ae06c.png&h=df42c0d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼日本男藝人今年入圍相當稀少，沒想到由前 KAT-TUN 成員赤西仁拿下 31 名，成為今年日本第一帥，也是員赤西仁目前為止的最高名次。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61036/5863257508a2c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61036%2F5863257508a2c.png&h=bdfffcb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼曾經拿下 2014 年冠軍的「霸道總裁」傑米道南（Jamie Dornan），今年獲得了 20 名。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61036/58632578bf20e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61036%2F58632578bf20e.png&h=bae1b235&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼全球男人憧憬的時尚模範碧咸，今年拿下了第 17 帥。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61036/5863257a1e00b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61036%2F5863257a1e00b.png&h=e8c9b875&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼韓國男團 BIGBANG 的人氣成員 T.O.P 帥氣的臉蛋加上高挑身材，在歐美一直也是韓國帥哥的代表，今年則拿下了 16 名。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61036/5863257b94eb5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61036%2F5863257b94eb5.png&h=b6457e82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼同樣正在服役的 Super Junior 始源今年落到了第 12 名。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61036/5863257d69477.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61036%2F5863257d69477.png&h=83969d1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼今年與泰勒絲上演了一齣熱戀到分手大戲的英國男演員湯姆&middot;希德斯頓，獲得了第 10 帥的封號。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61036/5863257f087f8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61036%2F5863257f087f8.png&h=9a47aeea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼《權力遊戲》男演員基特哈靈頓拿下了第 8 名。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61036/586325803dad3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61036%2F586325803dad3.png&h=a710ad7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼台灣男星拿下的最高名次，就是由高以翔獲得了第 7 名！近年來積極轉向美國發展的高以翔，一直都被美國媒體封為是極品亞洲帥哥。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61036/5863258183930.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61036%2F5863258183930.png&h=68eef5b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼他可能是世界最帥的 Gay，39 的麥特&middot;波莫是公認的男神，今年獲得了第 4 名。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61036/58632582cc098.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61036%2F58632582cc098.png&h=5aad00b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼BIGBANG 的成員太陽今年大躍進，從去年的第 24 名一口氣竄升到第 2 名，成為了今年的亞洲最帥！<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61036/58632585a156a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61036%2F58632585a156a.png&h=98ce10e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼今年的最帥臉孔冠軍就由荷蘭男星米契爾哈斯曼奪下，他在《權力遊戲》第四季接演了 Daario Naharis 這個角色，看過的劇迷肯定就知道他多有魅力。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61036/5863268a43c4b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61036%2F5863268a43c4b.png&h=a8476aca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Nzs0OJjkPik\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNzs0OJjkPik&d=wzNEviSXu2%2Bb%2FbVpVe2lf5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=e157e6a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Nzs0OJjkPik</a>"},{"pid":"bd6a16961dc2947006632a90e6556b640ead6296","tid":57501,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T05:42:07.000Z","msg":"冇我就知呢個唔準"},{"pid":"135018eacce4f8996b48ff8b953eb25a9b341d72","tid":57501,"uid":59659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T05:46:40.000Z","msg":"81同90幅相都幾衰下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eb426954437009d724f412ede0bda7101ff3341","tid":57501,"uid":17664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T05:49:04.000Z","msg":"大腸排第二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fe35c8ec785b83a0287008288e662d465959f65","tid":57501,"uid":21462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T05:54:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaGmKyXcCR5svihtbgjLAEpe3iTS85feWGwfSAwZ3DfEb?filename=757TLnc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F757TLnc.jpg&h=67666ffd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee6a929309fa246fa720502c2f16da0590291496","tid":57501,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T05:55:47.000Z","msg":"on9<br />\n<br />\n有亞洲人型過碧咸同狼人已經冇乜可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要係泡菜班花𡃁，邊個on9排架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e7cd2a95c443c5b22237153620e2c29fb6b4516","tid":57501,"uid":45505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T05:56:26.000Z","msg":"大腸咁不如鄭大世啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc217af4a99f99d702f1c6369e06fafeecdde18e","tid":57501,"